text: Anne de Ruiter (born 30 November 1999) is a Dutch professional racing cyclist. She signed to ride for the UCI Women's Team for the 2019 women's road cycling season, but ultimately did not ride in any races for the team, and left the team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
